name: "Good for you" Muesli
description: Eat a bowl of this each morning, and before you know it you will look just like the Swedish babe on the package.  Or maybe she's the prize inside the bag?  Ahhh..the days of cereal toys...

name: Kikori no Kirikabu
description:
The perfect northwest snack, this Japanese import was almost certainly inspired by 1,000-year-old cedars in Akita prefecture.  Makes you wonder, though:  if we're enjoying candy stumps, are there candy logs, branches, and pinecones somewhere out there maintaining balance in the universe?

More info, from the source:

小麦胚芽入りの香ばしいビスケットとミルクチョコレートの相性の良い組み合わせ。かわいらしい切株型のチョコスナックです。（栄養機能食品：カルシウム）
